name: Lip Plumping Oil
description:
Experience the transformative powers as it softens skin, diminishes lines, and amplifies volume, leaving you with irresistibly luscious, party-ready lips. Indulge in the luxurious water-shine effect, adorned with delicate glistening pearls that effortlessly catch and reflect light. Our lip plumping oil offers a silky, comfortable texture you'll absolutel adore day and night.

Ingredients: Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Octyldodecanol, Ethylene/Propylene/Styrene Copolymer, Polyisobutene, Diisostearyl Malate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Vanillin Butyl Ether, Capsicum Annuum (Paprika) Fruit Extract, Zingiber Officinale (Ginger) Root Extract, Fragrance, Red 7 Lake (CI 15850)
